### 2. Restrictions on Use
Regardless of your license tier, you may not:
* Decompile, reverse engineer, disassemble, or attempt to derive the source code of the compiled Cython mathematical engines (`.so` / `.pyd` files).
* Remove, alter, or obscure any proprietary notices, copyright labels, or watermark branding from the Software.
* Resell, lease, sublicense, or distribute the Software as a standalone commercial service or integrated API without explicit written consent.

